  "community": {
    "title": "What Our Community Says",
    "testimonial1": "The teachers here truly care about every student and go above and beyond to make sure they succeed. I have seen my child grow not only in academic performance but also in self-confidence, teamwork, and critical thinking. The personalized attention each student receives makes a huge difference in their overall development, and we are so grateful for this supportive community.",
    "author1": "Ahmed S.",
    "testimonial2": "This school provides an outstanding environment for learning. The modern teaching methods, combined with innovative technology and engaging activities, ensure that students are not just memorizing but actually understanding concepts deeply. My daughter has become more creative, more independent, and more excited about learning. The staff genuinely invests in every student’s success, and that makes all the difference.",
    "author2": "Sarah K.",
    "testimonial3": "Joining this school community was truly the best decision for our family. My children look forward to attending every day because the lessons are interactive, the teachers are approachable, and the atmosphere encourages curiosity and growth. Beyond academics, they are learning life skills such as responsibility, problem-solving, and empathy. I feel confident knowing they are in the best hands.",
    "author3": "Omar A."
  },
  "admission": {
    "title": "Admissions Made Simple",
